# Poetry Audio Directory

This directory contains audio files for poems and ghazals.

## Organization:
- Create subdirectories for each author using author ID
- Support for multiple languages (en/ur subdirectories)

## Structure:
```
poems/
├── {author-id}/
│   ├── en/
│   │   ├── {poem-id}.mp3
│   │   └── ...
│   └── ur/
│       ├── {poem-id}.mp3
│       └── ...
```

## Supported Formats:
- MP3 (recommended)
- WAV
- OGG
- AAC
